{"actor":"vitalitek/refinery","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-21T11:19:31Z","event_type":"updated","id":"8768d0f2-453c-4063-9070-ed6efba907a9","issue_id":"vi-54v","new_value":"{\"description\":\"BLOCKING: git fetch fails due to stale/wrong path references across the vitalitek git repo. Root cause: repo was moved from /Users/jeremy/vitalitek to /Users/jeremy/Documents/gt/vitalitek but path references were not updated.\\n\\nSymptoms:\\n1. .git file in refinery/rig pointed to /Users/jeremy/gt/vitalitek/.repo.git/worktrees/rig (FIXED this session)\\n2. .repo.git/worktrees/rig/gitdir pointed to /Users/jeremy/gt/vitalitek/refinery/rig/.git (FIXED this session)  \\n3. cardi/.git/objects/info/alternates pointed to /Users/jeremy/vitalitek/.git/objects (FIXED - now points to .repo.git/objects)\\n4. mayor/rig/.git/objects/info/alternates pointed to /Users/jeremy/vitalitek/.git/objects (FIXED - now points to .repo.git/objects)\\n5. .repo.git is a SHALLOW clone missing base objects: 2ddb101facd4b810470e1c12412b38f71a035765, 594c0e03190cd6d45b7b881df7168f6d34d666e3, c49dcfc2745a8b2f17f180bcc54597131b74d588 - these were previously stored in alternates at the old path.\\n\\ngit fetch --prune origin FAILS with: fatal: pack has 142 unresolved deltas. Cannot merge branches without git fetch working.\\n\\nFix needed: Either re-clone or repair the shallow pack - possibly: git clone --mirror github.com:outdoorsea/vitalitek.git to get full objects, then repair alternates chain.\",\"priority\":1}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"vi-54v\",\"title\":\"git fetch warning: stale worktree reference /Users/jeremy/gt/vitalitek/.repo.git/worktrees/rig\",\"description\":\"During git fetch --prune origin, consistently see: 'fatal: not a git repository: /Users/jeremy/gt/vitalitek/.repo.git/worktrees/rig'. The path does not exist. This is a stale worktree reference in the git config. Non-blocking but noisy.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-21T18:07:03Z\",